posting_body: ['WE HAVE A RENT TO OWN PROGRAM EASY TO  QUALIFY!', 'Quick move in.', 'If you are an independent worker have low credit or background issues and have problems finding a place to settle with your family, do not hesitate call me or TEXT me, I am a rental expert in South Florida, I will find a property for you and get you approved.', 'WE HAVE A RENT TO OWN PROGRAM with credit score of over 550, we will buy any property CASH for you  up tp $600,000 and then rent it to you for 1 to 3 years until you can get ready to purchase it, it will save some of your rent money towards the purchase ( about 25% of payment).', 'AMAZING 1 Bed 1 1/2 Bath Condo in the heart of Brickell.', 'Professionally designed with Turkish Marble floors throughout the unit including both bathrooms and granite kitchen countertops.', 'Come live in exclusive Brickell Key and enjoy the privacy and tranquility of the island.', 'Walking distance to Brickell City Center, Mary Brickell Village, Best Miami Restaurants, Shopping.', 'CALL ME OR TEXT ME', 'I RESPOND INMIDIATELLY!!', 'show contact info', ')', '""EASY SOLUTIONS REALTY LLC ""']
